name: Ashes to Ashes (to Ashes)
description: In Deadbolt, the death of a person define which undead they'll become: overdosed become zombies, death by toasters bath become skeletons, etc...Skeletons are always cold, which explains why they'd only wear thick clothes in that world. I loved the lore of that game and made several attempt at the reaper you control. This one is the latest.
